thread.title: Diana Containerships Expects Vessels To Be Delivered To The Buyer At Latest By Apr 27, 2018

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Diana Containerships Expects Vessels To Be Delivered To The Buyer At Latest By Apr 27, 2018
text:
March 1 (Reuters) - Diana Containerships Inc:
* PRESS RELEASE - DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS INC. ANNOUNCES THE SALE OF TWO PANAMAX CONTAINER VESSELS
* DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS INC - EXPECTS VESSELS TO BE DELIVERED TO THE BUYER AT LATEST BY APRIL 27, 2018
* DIANA CONTAINERSHIPS - ‍SIGNED,THROUGH 2 UNITS, 2 MEMORANDA OF AGREEMENT TO SELL M/V SAGITTA, M/V CENTAURUS, FOR $12.3 MILLION EACH​ Source text for Eikon:
